      "style": "accent",
      "content": "持続静注・スライディングスケール・基礎ボーラス法の実践ガイド",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-accent{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0d4a4a,#14b8a6);color:#fff}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700}.main{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;height:540px;padding:0 60px;gap:60px}.left-panel{flex:1}.right-panel{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center}h1{font-size:48px;font-weight:900;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:20px}.subtitle{font-size:24px;opacity:0.85;line-height:1.6}.tag{display:inline-block;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);padding:8px 20px;border-radius:20px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;margin-right:8px}.avatar-circle{width:200px;height:200px;border-radius:50%;border:4px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1)}.avatar-circle img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover}.author-name{font-size:24px;font-weight:700}.author-title{font-size:16px;opacity:0.8;text-align:center;line-height:1.5;margin-top:4px}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;opacity:0.6}</style><div class=\"slide slide-accent\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 1 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><div class=\"left-panel\"><h1>インスリン量の調整、<br>自信ありますか？</h1><div class=\"subtitle\">持続静注・スライディングスケール・<br>基礎ボーラス法の実践ガイド</div><div><span class=\"tag\">糖尿病</span><span class=\"tag\">インスリン</span><span class=\"tag\">病棟管理</span></div></div><div class=\"right-panel\"><div class=\"avatar-circle\"><img src=\"/dr-iwatatsu.png\" alt=\"Dr.いわたつ\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"></div><div class=\"author-name\">Dr.いわたつ</div><div class=\"author-title\">糖尿病専門医・指導医<br>内分泌専門医 / 医学博士</div></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 2,
      "title": "当直中、一番多い相談",
      "style": "dark",
      "content": "起：研修医が最も迷うインスリン調整",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-dark{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a1a1a,#132e2e);color:#fff}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.2);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#2dd4bf}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#94a3b8}.main{padding:30px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#2dd4bf;margin-bottom:30px}.alert-box{border-left:6px solid #14b8a6;background:rgba(20,184,166,0.08);padding:30px 36px;border-radius:0 16px 16px 0;margin-bottom:24px}.alert-box p{font-size:24px;line-height:1.7;color:#e2e8f0}.point-box{border-left:6px solid #ef4444;background:rgba(239,68,68,0.08);padding:24px 36px;border-radius:0 16px 16px 0;margin-top:20px}.point-box p{font-size:24px;line-height:1.7;color:#fca5a5;font-weight:700}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#64748b}</style><div class=\"slide slide-dark\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 2 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>当直中、一番多い相談</h2><div class=\"alert-box\"><p>「先生、この患者さんのインスリンどうしましょう？」<br><br>持続静注のレートは？<br>スライディングスケールでいい？<br>基礎ボーラスに切り替えるタイミングは？</p></div><div class=\"point-box\"><p>教科書には載っているけれど、<br>実際の患者を前にすると手が止まる</p></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 3,
      "title": "RABBIT 2試験が変えたエビデンス",
      "style": "light",
      "content": "承：基礎ボーラス法 vs スライディングスケール",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-light{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8fffe,#e6f7f5);color:#0a1a1a}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.15);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#0d4a4a}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a}.main{padding:30px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a;margin-bottom:24px}.card{border:2px solid rgba(20,184,166,0.3);border-radius:16px;padding:24px 30px;margin-bottom:16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.8)}.card-title{font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a;margin-bottom:8px}.card-body{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#334155}.highlight{color:#14b8a6;font-weight:700}.source{font-size:18px;color:#64748b;margin-top:16px}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8}</style><div class=\"slide slide-light\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 3 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>RABBIT 2 Surgery試験のデータ</h2><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">対象</div><div class=\"card-body\">外科入院2型糖尿病患者 <span class=\"highlight\">211例</span>（RCT）<br>グラルギン+グルリジン群 vs スライディングスケール群</div></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">血糖140 mg/dL未満の達成率</div><div class=\"card-body\">基礎ボーラス群 <span class=\"highlight\">55%</span> vs SSI群 <span class=\"highlight\">31%</span><br>1日インスリン量：BB群 42単位 vs SSI群 わずか12単位</div></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">臨床アウトカム</div><div class=\"card-body\">基礎ボーラス群で<span class=\"highlight\">手術合併症が有意に減少</span></div></div><div class=\"source\">出典：Umpierrez GE, et al. Diabetes Care 2011;34(2):256-261</div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 4,
      "title": "スライディングスケールの落とし穴",
      "style": "dark",
      "content": "転：SSI単独が非推奨となった理由",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-dark{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a1a1a,#132e2e);color:#fff}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.2);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#2dd4bf}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#94a3b8}.main{padding:30px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#2dd4bf;margin-bottom:24px}.list-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:18px}.list-num{font-size:26px;font-weight:900;color:#14b8a6;min-width:50px;margin-right:16px}.list-text{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#e2e8f0}.point-box{border-left:6px solid #ef4444;background:rgba(239,68,68,0.08);padding:20px 30px;border-radius:0 16px 16px 0;margin-top:20px}.point-box p{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#fca5a5;font-weight:700}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#64748b}</style><div class=\"slide slide-dark\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 4 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>SSI単独の問題点</h2><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">1</span><span class=\"list-text\">「後追い（reactive）」の治療 ── 高血糖が起きてから対応</span></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">2</span><span class=\"list-text\">基礎インスリンがないため血糖の乱高下が大きい</span></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">3</span><span class=\"list-text\">食間・夜間の血糖上昇を予防できない</span></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">4</span><span class=\"list-text\">SSI群のインスリン量は1日12単位 = 明らかに不足</span></div><div class=\"point-box\"><p>ADA 2025：SSI単独は「discouraged」<br>長期使用は「strongly discouraged」</p></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 5,
      "title": "実践：TDD計算と基礎ボーラス設定",
      "style": "light",
      "content": "結：明日から使える具体的アクション",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-light{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8fffe,#e6f7f5);color:#0a1a1a}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.15);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#0d4a4a}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a}.main{padding:20px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a;margin-bottom:20px}.list-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:14px}.list-num{font-size:26px;font-weight:900;color:#14b8a6;min-width:50px;margin-right:16px}.list-text{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#334155}.alert-box{border-left:6px solid #14b8a6;background:rgba(20,184,166,0.08);padding:18px 30px;border-radius:0 16px 16px 0;margin-top:16px}.alert-box p{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#334155}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8}</style><div class=\"slide slide-light\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 5 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>TDD計算と基礎ボーラス設定</h2><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">1</span><span class=\"list-text\">TDD = 体重 x 0.3-0.5 単位/kg/日で計算<br>（例：70kg x 0.4 = 28単位/日）</span></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">2</span><span class=\"list-text\">50:50ルールで分割<br>基礎14単位（グラルギン1日1回）+ 追加14単位（3食に分割）</span></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">3</span><span class=\"list-text\">補正係数 = 1800 / TDD<br>（例：1800/28 = 64 → 64mg/dL高いごとに1単位追加）</span></div><div class=\"alert-box\"><p>低血糖リスク因子（高齢・腎不全・肝不全）: 0.2-0.3単位/kg/日に減量<br>肥満・ステロイド使用: 0.5-0.6単位/kg/日に増量</p></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 6,
      "title": "Take Home Message",
      "style": "accent",
      "content": "3つの持ち帰りポイント",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-accent{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0d4a4a,#14b8a6);color:#fff}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700}.main{padding:30px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;gap:28px}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px}.thm-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.12);border-radius:20px;padding:28px 36px;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:20px}.thm-num{font-size:36px;font-weight:900;min-width:50px;opacity:0.7}.thm-text{font-size:26px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.5}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;opacity:0.6}</style><div class=\"slide slide-accent\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 6 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>Take Home Message</h2><div class=\"thm-card\"><span class=\"thm-num\">01</span><span class=\"thm-text\">SSI単独はADA 2025で非推奨。<br>基礎インスリンの土台が必須</span></div><div class=\"thm-card\"><span class=\"thm-num\">02</span><span class=\"thm-text\">TDD = 体重 x 0.3-0.5単位/kg/日<br>50:50で基礎:ボーラスに分割</span></div><div class=\"thm-card\"><span class=\"thm-num\">03</span><span class=\"thm-text\">IV→皮下移行は2時間overlap<br>1型では基礎投与前のIV中止は禁忌</span></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
